{"word":"Ezer","slug":"ezer","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ezer</b> <a href=\"#/H5827\">H5827</a><br/><a href=\"#/H5829\">H5829</a> <br/> 1. Called Ezar, a Horite duke<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=21'>Gen 36:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=27'>Gen 36:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=30'>Gen 36:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=38'>1Ch 1:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=42'>1Ch 1:42</a><br/> 2. A son of Ephraim<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=7&verse=21'>1Ch 7:21</a><br/> 3. A priest<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=42'>Neh 12:42</a><br/> 4. A man of Judah<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=4'>1Ch 4:4</a> <br/> - Perhaps identical with Ezra<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=17'>1Ch 4:17</a> <br/> 5. A Gadite warrior<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=9'>1Ch 12:9</a><br/> 6. A Levite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=3&verse=19'>Neh 3:19</a>"}]}